{"id":"errors/NG2009","title":"NG2009: 元件選擇器與影子 DOM 要求不對應。","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng2009-component-selector-does-not-match-shadow-dom-requirements\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"78tq1a1tayly9wjhzxtafjta0\">NG2009: 元件選擇器與影子 DOM 要求不對應。<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG2009#ng2009-component-selector-does-not-match-shadow-dom-requirements\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  \n  \n\n  <div class=\"error-description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG2009#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"f03cae6j7gsz0ww1uejdrdod0\">使用 <code><a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation.ShadowDom</a></code> 的元件的選擇器與自定義元素標記名稱的要求不對應。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d0z9edu8zvgrbldsrgm8dt4fe\">為了使標籤名稱被視為有效的自定義元素名稱，它必須：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1r1nqq8w0n0125nss7h5cf1s0\">是小寫的。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d16rai78aihqfas42wakzvfn8\">包含連字元。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9j3t518812kvnamt3xvxoqzi7\">以字母（a-z）開頭。</li>\n</ul>\n\n  </div>\n\n\n  \n  <br>\n\n  <div class=\"debugging\">\n    <h2 id=\"debugging-the-error\">如何排除本錯誤<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG2009#debugging-the-error\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9q3lu9lvgz7jm0cym65r4vp51\">重新命名元件的選擇器，使其符合要求。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9uaf4w2mfc4bmjwfg76el4q4p\"><strong>之前：</strong></p>\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'comp',\n  encapsulation: <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation.ShadowDom</a>\n  …\n})\n\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3s2h6p2y5qkyl4avo82t6rkg9\"><strong>之後：</strong></p>\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app-comp',\n  encapsulation: <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewEncapsulation.ShadowDom</a>\n  …\n})\n\n</code-example>\n\n  </div>\n  \n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - errors\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#ShadowDom\n - errors/NG2009#debugging-the-error\n - errors/NG2009#description\n - errors/NG2009#ng2009-component-selector-does-not-match-shadow-dom-requirements\n-->"}